---
/**
 * CTA Component - Brutalist Style
 */
---

<section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-void);">
  <div class="container cta-shell">
    <div class="cta-panel">
      <div class="cta-copy">
        <span class="label-mono block mb-4">// Next Step</span>
        <h2 class="mb-6">
          See how Pixelated Empathy fits your training workflow.
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Use it for individual practice, supervision, or team-based simulation.
          Start with a scenario, review the feedback, and decide whether it
          belongs in your clinical training stack.
        </p>
        <p class="cta-subcopy">
          Best fit for therapists, trainees, supervisors, and mental health
          organizations building repeatable skill development.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-terminal">
          Start Practice
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline"> Contact Sales </a>
        <a href="/demo-hub" class="btn btn-ghost"> Watch Demo </a>

        <p class="cta-meta">
          No credit card required for trial • Built for high-stakes conversation
          practice
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-shell {
    max-width: 72rem;
  }

  .cta-panel {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.15fr) minmax(18rem, 0.85fr);
    gap: var(--space-8);
    align-items: center;
    border: var(--border-primary);
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.06), transparent 40%),
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .cta-copy {
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .cta-subcopy {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .cta-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cta-panel {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta-actions {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .cta-actions .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
